Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:46.71,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No matter what happens, It’s OK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:48.25,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because we are the best
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:49.46,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We are the best!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:52.22,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Nobody can ever stop us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:53.84,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because we are the best!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.09,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now, touch the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:56.35,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}ビルディング伸びる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.35,0:01:59.56,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}狭い空見上げ Close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:03.06,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The next moment 広がる世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:06.11,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}踏み出せば I’ll have a new experience
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:07.69,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We go back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:09.03,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But we are who we are
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:11.82,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}見失わず 前へ Go on!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.82,0:02:13.20,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Count on you, flyin’ up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:17.53,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Anywhere, we can handle everything so well
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:18.99,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}常に冷静に Manage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:20.66,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}平凡な檻からFly away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:21.70,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just like a business
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.21,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}世界を見極め Negotiate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.21,0:02:25.96,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}To live is continuously to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:29.55,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Until I die, no end in sight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:31.30,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I believe in our bond
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:34.09,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}繋がってる　確かなパス
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:36.89,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your power still flows into me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:40.72,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}感じてる　大切なものをこの肩に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.23,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}きみとならFly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:46.69,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I decided to become a sage of the stars, oh like you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.57,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh oh (Push forward!! Pu- Push forward!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:52.61,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh oh (Flyin’ high!! Fl- Flyin’ high!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:55.74,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}止まる事ない二つのタイムライン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:58.32,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}変えていく　さあ二人でRight now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:02:59.83,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:01.08,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What can I do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.16,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go on! Go on!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:07.13,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}何処までもきみとFly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:46.71,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}无论发生什么 都没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:48.25,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为我们是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:49.46,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们是最好的!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:52.22,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有人能阻挡我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:53.84,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为我们是最好的!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.09,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在让我们触摸天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:56.35,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大楼不断向前延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.35,0:01:59.56,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}仰望狭窄的天空 闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:03.06,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}下一刻 是更广阔的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:06.11,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只要向前踏出一步 就能有全新的体验
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:07.69,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们不断折返
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:09.03,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我们就是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:11.82,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不忘初心 继续前行!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.82,0:02:13.20,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}依靠你 飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:17.53,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}无论何地 我们都能将完美处理一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:18.99,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}时刻保持冷静地管理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:20.66,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}飞离平凡的牢笼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:21.70,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就像是做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.21,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}洞察世界以此谈判
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.21,0:02:25.96,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}生活就是不断地学习
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:29.55,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}直至死亡 都无法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:31.30,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我相信我们的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:34.09,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那真实连结着的纽带
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:36.89,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的力量依然流淌在我的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:40.72,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我能感受到 肩负着重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.23,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}与你一起飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:46.69,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我决定成为星之贤者 就如你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.57,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}噢噢（向前推进!!向前推进!!）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:52.61,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}噢噢（飞向高空!!飞向高空!!）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:55.74,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}两条永不停止的时间线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:58.32,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我们两人一起改变 就是现在!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:02:59.83,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我能为你做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:01.08,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我能与你做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.16,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}继续前进！继续前进!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:07.13,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}与你一起飞翔到任何地方
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED「曖昧ガール」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:35.94,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Life is wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:46.03,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Ah！キミがいない日々は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:49.83,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ピンクのない桜の花みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:52.21,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}No！それはいや
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.21,0:21:55.92,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}わたしはもう恋をしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:59.80,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ハローハロー　コイワズライさん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:03.05,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}甘酸っぱいスイーツランチタイム
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:07.18,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}日曜日の午後はまた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:11.02,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}高鳴る鼓動が痛い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.02,0:22:14.52,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}水たまりをジャンプして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.65,0:22:17.65,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}今日はどこでなにしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.65,0:22:19.53,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ホントはずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.53,0:22:23.41,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ふたりでいたいのに（だめ?）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:26.87,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}曖昧な距離感でどうしようって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.87,0:22:28.83,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}どうしたいってmisty days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.83,0:22:32.12,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ときめいて強がって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:34.42,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ハッとしてパニック!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:37.79,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ドキドキがバレちゃう、キミに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:40.84,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}曖昧じゃ大胆にいかないし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.84,0:22:42.92,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}あたりまえにone-way-love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:46.18,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}恋の途中はいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.18,0:22:50.89,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ココロとカラダが（今日も）反比例
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:54.10,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}わたし　曖昧ガール
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:35.94,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}人生是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:46.03,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}啊！没有你的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:49.83,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}就像是失去粉色的樱花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:52.21,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}不！绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.21,0:21:55.92,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}我已坠入爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:59.80,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}你好你好 陷入相思的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:03.05,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}酸甜点心的午餐时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:07.18,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}星期日的中午
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:11.02,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}激动的心跳感到疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.02,0:22:14.52,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}一下跳过水洼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.65,0:22:17.65,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}今天要在哪里做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.65,0:22:19.53,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}其实的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.53,0:22:23.41,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}一直想要和你两人独处（不行吗?）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:26.87,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}在暧昧的距离感下该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.87,0:22:28.83,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}想要做些什么 在迷茫的日子里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.83,0:22:32.12,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}那强烈的悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:34.42,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}惊觉的我陷入恐慌!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:37.79,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}被你发现那惊慌失措的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:40.84,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}暧昧又不能过于大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.84,0:22:42.92,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}理所当然的单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:46.18,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}在恋爱的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.18,0:22:50.89,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}内心和行动（今天也）呈现反比
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:54.10,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}我就是暧昧女孩
